Set in one of Canggu’s most desirable neighborhoods, it’s just minutes from beaches, cafés, and sunset spots. Whether as your tropical retreat or high-performing rental, this loft combines modern design, privacy, and unbeatable location.

property_description: A stylish modern villa designed for relaxed living and work-life balance. With two bedrooms, enclosed living, a private pool, and a bright home office, this turnkey property combines comfort and practicality. Fully furnished with quality finishes, it sits in a quiet pocket of Uluwatu — minutes from surf, dining, and beach clubs. Perfect for long-term living or rental investment in one of Bali’s most desirable coastal hubs.

property_description: A sunlit Mediterranean-style villa in Kedungu featuring a private pool, rooftop terrace, and serene views of rice fields and the ocean. Just two minutes from Joshua District and Kedungu Beach, this 2-bedroom home captures the soul of Bali’s west coast — elegant, peaceful, and artfully designed. Fully furnished and turnkey ready, it’s a perfect blend of charm, location, and value.

property_description: Nestled among Ubud’s peaceful rice fields, these brand-new 2-bedroom villas blend modern design with natural serenity. Each home features a rooftop patio ideal for yoga or sunset gatherings, a private pool, and spacious enclosed living. Built in 2024 within a family-friendly cluster, these villas offer flexible ownership options (freehold or leasehold) and a rare balance of tranquility, functionality, and investment value in central Ubud.
